title: Mayors Stimulus-Water Projects 2009
name: Mayors Stimulus-Water Projects 2009
description: This data represents the count of water projects by city for the 2009 Mayors Stimulus Report from the US Conference of Mayors. The data was calculated using a pivot table to find counts of total water projects, sum of funding, and sum of jobs created for cities across the United States. Locations were then geocoded using batchgeocode.com and uploaded as a csv.
